⚡ snapapp 0.4.0 - Snapshot application

USAGE:
    snapapp [OPTIONS] [format] <COMMAND>

ARGUMENTS:
    format
        Output format
        Choices: json, toml

OPTIONS:
    -v, --verbose
        Enable verbose output
    -h, --help
        Print help information
    -V, --version
        Print version information

COMMANDS:
    serve
        Run the server
    help
        Show help information
    version
        Show version information
    completion
        Generate shell completion scripts
